TopicTitle: Waiter, theres a _____________ in my soup!

Articles.Content:
You ordered stink soup.

Waiter, in my soup is a bowl containing my soup, with the bowl containing my soup, ad infinitum!

Huh, I'll check on that. *hears in the distance* HEY! Yeah, you! How did TARDIS feed get into that man's soup? Your fired!

 

Waiter! My soup is literally garbage!

Sorry. 

You are what you eat. #shotsfired

 

Waiter! There's razor blades in my soup!

Well, someone has to cut your beard…

Waiter, there's an unladen african swallow in my soup!

AUUUUUUUUUUUUUUUUUUGGGGGGGGGGGHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHH

Waiter, the poster above me has 1/10.17 the rep I do!

That's not a soup. Buh-bye!

Waiter, there's a microverse in my soup!

No, that's your colon. HOW DO OUR CUSTOMERS COLONS GET IN THEIR SOUPS ANYHOW?! I QUIT! *walks out door*

 

Waiter! My soup is an Irish youtuber!

That's a pretty rare sight.

Waiter, there's a dead rat in my soup!

Probably it died because it tried the soup 

Waiter, my soup has been modded to the point at which it runs at 3 fps.

Ctrl-Alt-Del! Ctrl-Alt-Del! Ctrl-Alt-Del! Damn!! Restart PC... Shutdown PC.

Waiter there Bonkers D. Bobcat in my soup!

What? Huh? How...but...real...life... ... ...SCREW THIS! *throws your table out window, then proceeds to jump through it*

 

Waiter! My soup is half machine!

No, the soup is sitting inside an exosuit. Don't forget the difference between an exosuit and a cyborg!

Waiter, there's mountain dew and doritos in my soup!

You did order the MLG special, correct?

Waiter, my bowl is empty but it's raining soup outside!

Huh. Should be raining tacos.

Waiter! It's high noon in my soup!

Start duel with soup!

Waiter! There Mystery Shack in my soup!

Wait, are you serio- *proceeds to be eaten by a creature of unimaginable horror and wonder, as the customer has to watch the whole thing*

 

Waiter! It's low midnight in my soup!

No, its high noon in your soup. Quickly, go hide somewhere!

Waiter, there's a dead Overwatch meme in my soup! I thought I buried them!

Edited September 16, 2016 by ZentroCatson

Well, sometimes we lose track of them, you know?

Soup, there's a waiter in my fly!

Darn it, @MDZhB, look at what you've done.

 

Waiter, there's an unexpected lump of animal cells from a previously alive organism from the Muscidae family which recently had its biological functions ceased due to being unable to extract dioxygen from the layer of gasses surrounding this 12,742 km wide lump of mass in which our organisms are currently located in my solution (composed of mainly nutrients, plant cells, lipids, sodium chloride and dihydrogen monoxide), which is contained within a solid semi-sphere made out of metallic compounds.

Edited September 17, 2016 by Guest

Sounds like a fly. Eat up!

Waiter, AT&T only let me download half of my soup!

Here, have a Verizon to finish your download.

 

Waiter! My soup is making terrible puns in a goofy font!

What's goofy? This isn't goofy font! It's COMICAL! HAHAHAHAHAHAHAHA!

Waiter, my soup voided my bowl's warranty!

No receipt, no refund. No money back guarantee either...
 

Waiter, there's a politician in my soup!"

Burn him!

Waiter, there's homework in my soup!

*eats homework* Now you just have to tell your teacher that your waiter ate your homework.

Waiter, my soup can't be factored any further!
